\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The Peritum Agri Institute is not yet registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training and has no programmes accredited by the CHE. \line \line The Institution is applying for accreditation of a Postgraduate Diploma in Entrepreneurial Sustainable Urban Agriculture which will be offered in the distance mode of delivery at -Main Campus - Bloemfontein.\line \line The Institution has also applied for accreditation of the following programmes which are still in process\'3A\line \line - Diploma Agriculture Production and Management H\'2FPR1060\'2FE002CAN \'28Contact mode\'29\line - Advanced Diploma Climate Smart Agriculture H\'2FPR1060\'2FE003CAN \'28Contact mode\'29\line \line This is the first application from the Institution.\line \cell \pard 

